FROM "DbWT37H1KogakuGassanaJikofutangaku" AS "DbWT37H1" LEFT JOIN( SELECT A.* FROM( SELECT "DbT3070".*, row_number() OVER (PARTITION BY "DbT3070"."hihokenshaNo", "DbT3070"."taishoNendo", "DbT3070"."hokenshaNo", "DbT3070"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" ORDER BY "DbT3070"."rirekiNo" DESC ) AS rowNum FROM rgdb."DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" AS "DbT3070" ) AS A WHERE A."dataSakuseiKubun" = '1' AND A."shomeisho_UketoriYM" is null OR A."shomeisho_UketoriYM" = '' AND A."hoseiZumi_SofuYM" is not null AND A."hoseiZumi_SofuYM" <> '' AND A.rowNum = 1 )AS "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku" ON "DbWT37H1"."hokenshaNoIn" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hihokenshaNo" AND "DbWT37H1"."taishoNendo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."taishoNendo" AND "DbWT37H1"."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."hokenshaNo" AND "DbWT37H1"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" = "DbT3070KogakuGassanJikoFutanGaku"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo"
